{"type": "article", "id": 4958, "title": "nanamica  2015 春季包袋系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-06T07:58:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 11, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233519fdAeNWt4j5S3zDLB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t日本人气户外品牌 nanamica 近日发布了其最新的 2015 春季包袋系列，包括 Cordura Cycling Pack，Two Way Duffle Bag，Two Way Tote Bag，Cordura Briefcase 和 Cordura Day Pack 等 5 种款式。设计团队采用了质轻又耐磨的帆布与过胶尼龙材质，搭配以温暖清新的色调。再加上日系品牌一贯对于细节的精细处理，使得这一系列的包袋兼具时尚与功能性。定价 299－409 美元（约合人民币 1860－2544 元）不等，<a href=\"http://www.endclothing.com/brands/nanamica\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233516dO3ZmCWcFVsaE0ou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335175IbcetK9W8rG6z4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233517HU1E3ZYeivsm6Px0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233518Cx5SZKH8qfdbcaO9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233518I3sniAUTVXC0qJcS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233518g6YZ12wsu0nKOy7l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}